name: FNeuralProfileStruct
doc: struct with all the settings we want in UNeuralProfile, separate to make it easer to pass this data around in the engine.

InputFormat:
Define the expected input format, if any output from material is not this format, a custom conversion
will be applied for this conversion.
OutputFormat:
Define the expected output format. A conversion between the output format and the actual format will
be applied automatically.
RuntimeType: runtime type (support "NNERuntimeRDGDml" only at this moment)
NNEModelData: Stores the NNEModelData imported from e.g., onnx model
InputDimension: Input dimension of the NNEModelData model
OutputDimension: Output dimension of the NNEModelData model
BatchSizeOverride: Used to override the batch size if the batch dimension is dynamic (-1)
TileSize: Total tiles used. Each tile will be executed by 1 batch
TileOverlap: Tile border overlaps (Left|Right, Top|Bottom). The larger this value, the more tiles are required to cover the whole screen when TileSize is Auto.
